Frequently Asked
Questions

Dynamic Merchant Solutions is committed to providing you with the best possible customer service. If you need additional support, please contact us at info@maildms.com or (800) 340-3671.

Table of Contents

Signing Up
Device Setup
Pricing
How do I sign up with Dynamic Merchant Solutions?

Please reach out to our sales team to begin your application. Once you have been approved, your sales rep will walk you through the process of selecting your necessary hardware, POS, and other needs, depending on your business.

Do I need a merchant account?

Yes, you must open a merchant account with Dynamic Merchant Solutions in order to process payments through our network.

Can I accept credit cards without buying your hardware?

Yes, we offer payment solutions that work with your existing hardware. Talk to our experts for complete details.

How long does it take to receive hardware?

Once your application is approved, we’ll ship your new system overnight within one business day.

How fast will I get paid?

The timing of deposits depends on your bank. You should generally see deposits in your account within 1–3 business days.

I’m having trouble setting up my system, how can I fix this?

Please call our customer service team at (800) 340-3671. They are available 24/7 to help you with any hardware or software issues you may encounter.

How can I add more devices or accessories to my existing system?

To add accessories or devices to your system, contact your account manager. Please contact us at info@maildms.com or (800) 340-3671.

How much will I pay in fees?

Your fees depend on the card types you charge and may even be impacted by your business type, if you’re considered a high risk industry. To get an exact quote, please contact our sale team at info@maildms.com or (800) 340-3671.

There’s an unexpected charge on my account, how do I find out more information?

If you have reviewed your statement and still have questions, please contact us at info@maildms.com or (800) 340-3671.

I am getting chargebacks, how can I resolve this?

If a cardholder or issuer disputes a transaction, you may receive a chargeback. If you receive a chargeback, we will notify you with details about the chargeback and advise you on next steps.

I think there are fraudulent transactions on my account, how can I resolve this?

Please reach out to our customer service team so we can review the fraudulent transaction details and determine next steps. Contact us at info@maildms.com or (800) 340-3671
